tasks.description: Get input to provision application in a BIG-IP LTM with pool,pool members, montiors,etc..

fields.fieldScript: Get vips available in the Partition

fieldScripts.scriptName: Get vips available in the Partition

tasks.scriptContent:
sys.path.insert(0,AVX::HELPER)
sys.path.insert(0,AVX::DEPENDENCIES)
import json
import requests
import Decrypt_Python3 as Decrypt
from requests.auth import HTTPBasicAuth
from base64 import b64encode
import appviewx
null = None
action = "<%action%>"
partition_type = '<%partition_type%>' if action == 'Create' else 'Existing Partition'
tenant_name = "<%new_partition_name%>" if partition_type != 'Existing Partition' else '<%Partition%>'
device_name = '<%device_name%>'
application_name = '<%virtual_server_name%>' if action == "Create" else '<%mod_virtual_server_name%>'
virtual_server_ip = '<%virtual_server_ip%>'
virtual_server_port = '<%virtual_server_port%>'



snat_pool = '<%snat_pool%>'


client_ssl = '<%client_ssl_profile%>'
client_ssl_name = '<%client_ssl_name%>'
client_ssl_private_key = '<%client_ssl_private_key%>'
client_ssl_certificate = '<%client_ssl_certificate%>'

server_ssl = '<%server_ssl_profile%>'
server_ssl_name='<%server_ssl_name%>'
server_ssl_certificate = '<%server_ssl_certificate%>'
server_ssl_private_key = '<%server_ssl_private_key%>'

monitor= '<%monitor%>'
monitor_type = '<%monitor_type%>'
monitor_name = '<%monitor_name%>'
monitor_send_string = '<%monitor_send_string%>'
monitor_recv_string = '<%monitor_receive_string%>'


persistence = '<%Persistence%>'
persistence_name = '<%persistence_name%>'
persistence_method = '<%persistence_method%>'

cookie = '<%Cookie%>'
cookie_name = '<%cookie_name%>'
cookie_method = '<%cookie_method%>'

associate_asm_policy = '<%associate_asm_policy>'
asm_policy = '<%asm_policy%>'

associate_afm_policy = '<%associate_afm_policy>'
afm_policy = '<%afm_policy%>'

pool_name = '<%pool_name%>' if action == 'Create' else '<%mod_pool_name%>'
pool_mem_ip = '<%pool_member_ips%>'
pool_mem_port = '<%pool_member_service_port%>'
pool_mem_tabular_input = <%pool_members%>


# Auth Header
connect_db = appviewx.db_connection()
device_db = connect_db.appviewx.device
device_data = [x for x in device_db.find({"name":device_name}) ][0]
device_ip = str(device_data["ip"])
username, password = Decrypt.getpassword(device_name)
end_point_url = "https://"+device_ip+"/mgmt/shared/appsvcs/declare"
userpass = username + ":" + password
userAndPass = b64encode(userpass.encode("utf-8")).decode("ascii")
headers = 'Basic %s' %  userAndPass

def get_list_of_values(comma_sep_values):
	'''
		Will Return a list of values from a comma separated string.
	'''
	
	if comma_sep_values:
		return comma_sep_values.split(',')
	return None
	
def get_pool_members():
	pool_mem_list = []
	if pool_mem_tabular_input != None and len(pool_mem_tabular_input) > 0:
		for each_row in pool_mem_tabular_input:
			pool_mem_list.append({"servicePort": int(each_row["pool_member_service_port"]),"serverAddresses": get_list_of_values(each_row["pool_member_ips"])})
	else:
		pool_mem_list.append({"servicePort": int(pool_mem_port),"serverAddresses": get_list_of_values(pool_mem_ip)})
		
	return pool_mem_list
	

def get_basic_payload():
	basic_create_payload = {  
	   "class": "AS3",
	   "action": "deploy",
	   "persist": True,
	   "declaration": {
		  "class": "ADC",
		  "schemaVersion": "3.11.0",
		  "label": "Sample 1",
		  "remark": "Simple HTTP application with RR pool",
		   tenant_name: {
			 "class": "Tenant",
			 application_name: {
				"class": "Application",
				"template": "generic",
				 application_name: {
				   "class": "Service_HTTP",
				   "snat":snat_pool,
				   "virtualAddresses": get_list_of_values(virtual_server_ip),
				   "virtualPort" : int(virtual_server_port),
				   "pool": pool_name
				},
				pool_name: {
				   "class": "Pool",
				   "monitors": ["http"] if monitor == "No" else [{"use":monitor_name}],
				   "members": get_pool_members()
				}
			 }
		  }
	   }
	}
	return basic_create_payload


def get_monitor_payload():
	monitor_payload = {}
	monitor_payload["class"] = "Monitor"
	monitor_payload["monitorType"] = monitor_type
	monitor_payload["receive"] = monitor_recv_string
	monitor_payload["send"] = monitor_send_string
	return monitor_payload

def get_tls_data(class_type,cert_name):
	tls = {}
	tls["class"] = class_type
	tls["certificates"] = [{"certificate": cert_name }]
	return tls

def get_server_certificate_payload():
	server_certificate_payload = {}
	server_certificate_payload["class"]= "Certificate"
	server_certificate_payload["remark"]= "in practice we recommend using a passphrase"
	server_certificate_payload["certificate"]= server_ssl_certificate
	server_certificate_payload["privateKey"]=server_ssl_private_key
	server_certificate_payload["passphrase"]=  {"ciphertext": "ZjVmNQ==","protected": "eyJhbGciOiJkaXIiLCJlbmMiOiJub25lIn0"}
	return server_certificate_payload

		
def get_client_certificate_payload():
	client_certificate_payload = {}
	client_certificate_payload["class"] = "Certificate"
	client_certificate_payload["remark"] = "in practice we recommend using a passphrase"
	client_certificate_payload["certificate"] = client_ssl_certificate
	client_certificate_payload["privateKey"] = client_ssl_private_key
	client_certificate_payload["passphrase"] =  {"ciphertext": "ZjVmNQ==","protected": "eyJhbGciOiJkaXIiLCJlbmMiOiJub25lIn0"}
	return client_certificate_payload


def get_persistence_payload():
	persistence_payload = {}
	persistence_payload["class"] = "Persist"
	persistence_payload["persistenceMethod"] = persistence_method
	if persistence_method == 'cookie':
		persistence_payload["cookieMethod"] = cookie_method
		persistence_payload["cookieName"] = cookie_name
		
	return persistence_payload

def get_modify_payload(create_payload):
	modify_payload= {}
	modify_payload["class"] = "AS3"
	modify_payload["action"] = "patch"
	modify_payload["schemaVersion"]="3.11.0"
	modify_payload["persist"] = True
	modify_payload["patchBody"] = [{"op": "add","path": "/" + tenant_name + "/" + application_name}]
	modify_payload["patchBody"][0]["value"] = create_payload["declaration"][tenant_name][application_name]
	return modify_payload
	


def get_create_payload():
	final_payload_for_creation = get_basic_payload()
	
	if monitor == "Yes":
		final_payload_for_creation["declaration"][tenant_name][application_name][monitor_name] = get_monitor_payload()
		
	if server_ssl == "Yes":
		cert_name = server_ssl_name + "_cert"
		final_payload_for_creation["declaration"][tenant_name][application_name][application_name]["class"] = "Service_HTTPS"
		final_payload_for_creation["declaration"][tenant_name][application_name][application_name]["serverTLS"] = server_ssl_name
		final_payload_for_creation["declaration"][tenant_name][application_name][server_ssl_name] = get_tls_data("TLS_Server",cert_name)
		final_payload_for_creation["declaration"][tenant_name][application_name][cert_name] = get_server_certificate_payload()
		
	if client_ssl == "Yes":
		cert_name = client_ssl_name + "_cert"
		final_payload_for_creation["declaration"][tenant_name][application_name][application_name]["class"] = "Service_HTTPS"
		final_payload_for_creation["declaration"][tenant_name][application_name][application_name]["clientTLS"] = client_ssl_name
		final_payload_for_creation["declaration"][tenant_name][application_name][client_ssl_name] = get_tls_data("TLS_Client",cert_name)
		final_payload_for_creation["declaration"][tenant_name][application_name][cert_name] = get_client_certificate_payload()
		
	if associate_asm_policy == "Yes":
		final_payload_for_creation["declaration"][tenant_name][application_name][application_name]["policyWAF"] =  { "bigip": "/Common/"+asm_policy }
		
	if associate_afm_policy == "Yes":
		final_payload_for_creation["declaration"][tenant_name][application_name][application_name]["Pointer_Firewall_Policy"] =  { "bigip": "/Common/"+ afm_policy }
	
	if persistence == "Yes":
		final_payload_for_creation["declaration"][tenant_name][application_name][application_name]["persistenceMethods"]= [{"use": persistence_name}]
		final_payload_for_creation["declaration"][tenant_name][application_name][persistence_name] =  get_persistence_payload()
	
	if action == "Modify" or partition_type == 'Existing Partition':
		final_payload_for_creation = get_modify_payload(final_payload_for_creation)
		
	return final_payload_for_creation

x = get_create_payload()
# AVX::LOG(str(json.dumps(x,sort_keys=False , indent =4)))

output = x["patchBody"][0]


AVX::OUTPUT({"output":output["value"],"payload_data":x,"end_point_url":end_point_url,"auth_header":headers})
